00:19:29.439 --> 00:19:35.239
For example, predicting one player in his 12th season and another in his third?

00:19:35.280 --> 00:19:44.000
So the length of the season, remember we intentionally used that common length of window, remember,

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:50.000
